Series NCJ2 single rod, double acting, miniature cylinders. Available in bore sizes 6, 10, 16mm and stroke lengths up to 8&quot;. Basic, foot, front flange and double rear clevis mounting options. Auto-switch capable. Other optional features include rubber bumpers and port location.
&lt;/p&gt;

